/#
 The compounding calculation method
 #/
enum FpML5.confirmation.CompoundingMethodEnum {
    # Flat compounding. Compounding excludes the spread. Note that the first compounding period has it's interest calculated including any spread then subsequent periods compound this at a rate excluding the spread.
    Flat 
    # No compounding is to be applied.
    None 
    # Straight compounding. Compounding includes the spread.
    Straight 
    # Spread Exclusive compounding.
    SpreadExclusive 

}

Flat.Doc: Flat compounding. Compounding excludes the spread. Note that the first compounding period has it's interest calculated including any spread then subsequent periods compound this at a rate excluding the spread.
Flat.Name: Flat

None.Doc: No compounding is to be applied.
None.Name: None

Straight.Doc: Straight compounding. Compounding includes the spread.
Straight.Name: Straight
